ute or storage capacity). For certain services offered as a fixed quantity over a specified term, revenue is recognized ratably over the contract term.\n*   **AI and Machine Learning Focus:** AWS\'s business model is heavily tied to advancing technology, including artificial intelligence and machine learning. In fact, effective January 1, 2025, Amazon shortened the estimated useful life of a subset of its servers and networking equipment from six years to five years specifically due to the increased pace of AI and ML technology development. This change alone increased depreciation expense by $1.4 billion in 2025, primarily impacting the AWS segment.',
